(This project aims to create an interactive web application using Hugging Face Transformers to demystify) Tj
T* (vision models and Large Language Models \(LLMs\) for beginners. The application will allow users to upload) Tj
T* (images, process them with various vision transformers, and then use an LLM to interpret the visual analysis,) Tj
T* (all while providing clear, step-by-step explanations and visualizations. It targets beginner-level students,) Tj
T* (developers, and researchers interested in gaining hands-on experience with these powerful AI tools in an) Tj
T* (educational context.) Tj
ET
